data.description: Welcome home to this beautifully renovated and nearly-1500 sqft 3 bedroom, 2 bath home in Port Orange, FL!! This block home is located close to shopping and amenities, yet on a quiet sidewalk-lined street with no HOA. Recent updates include 2023 HVAC, all new kitchen cabinetry with new appliances, Samsung Thinq washer & dryer, quartz countertops & subway-tiled backsplash, vinyl flooring throughout the home, interior paint, and so much more! Other features of the home include a full 2-car garage, fully fenced yard, and screened back porch. Enjoy endless adventures amongst some of Florida's most beautiful beaches and waterways just around the corner!
